txt.en: Many prisoner voices wail through the walls of Naerband. Perhaps if you could find some jailer keys, you might be able to let loose some of the denizens of Naerband.
Naerband is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should collect keys from jailers in Naerband.
Attempted to free many prisoners in Naerband.
Naerband is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should collect keys from jailers in Naerband.
The prison fortress of Naerband is populated by vile acts and jailed denizens.

After opening numerous prison doors to free prisoners in Naerband, you realize that Thraknûl is not just capturing Nurnhoth, but also many of the Orcs and Uruks formerly under the command of Sauron. Either Thraknûl is vying for power or he has gone mad.
